				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/%E1%BA%A4t-H%E1%BB%A3i-thu-s%C6%A1-t%C3%A0i-ch%C3%ADnh-b%E1%BB%99-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng-H%E1%BB%AFu-Nguy%C3%AAn-H%E1%BB%93-%C4%90%E1%BA%AFc-Kh%E1%BA%A3i-ti%C3%AAn-sinh-du-B%E1%BA%A1ch-M%C3%A3-s%C6%A1n-tr%E1%BB%8Bch-th%E1%BB%8B-giai-t%C3%A1c/poem-MX1ynTXruKLb82VGsDZuwQ">Ất Hợi thu sơ tài chính bộ trưởng Hữu Nguyên Hồ Đắc Khải tiên sinh du Bạch Mã sơn trịch thị giai tác hoạ vận dĩ thù - 乙亥秋初財政部長友元胡得愷先生遊白馬山擲示佳作和韻以酬</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Canh-T%C3%BD-xu%C3%A2n/poem-07lW8--tX-z2RUCwEm7SdQ">Canh Tý xuân - 庚子春</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/%C4%90%C3%B4ng-nguy%E1%BB%87t-%C4%91%C3%A0o-hoa-b%E1%BB%99-Minh-Ch%C3%A2u-nguy%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-vpwH6vWW_G1gId7cF5yYhw">Đông nguyệt đào hoa, bộ Minh Châu nguyên vận - 冬月桃花和明州原韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/H%E1%BB%93i-tr%E1%BA%A1o/poem-qeP_kb_yUSYlzh8F95bgrQ">Hồi trạo - 回棹</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-C%E1%BA%A9n/L%E1%BB%A5c-th%E1%BA%ADp-t%E1%BB%B1-thu%E1%BA%ADt/poem-qMR1OQDdKVeGZX82ZHVIwA">Lục thập tự thuật - 六述十自</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-C%E1%BA%A9n/author-YRtbQ4Y_EBSiaNimbo26Cg">Lê Khắc Cẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.ne